Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:15.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I wanna talk with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.81,0:22:19.61,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}待ち合わせは何時？（10時）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:21.77,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}駅前に集合（OK！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:25.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}着いたら教えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:27.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}使い慣れたスタンプで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:29.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}話合えちゃうスタンスが本当
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:33.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}心地良くて愛しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:37.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}一人胸にしまいこんだ言葉も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:41.96,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}上手くいかない減らない悩み事も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:48.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}全部忘れて遊びに行きたいね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:54.89,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}心のメモリア
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:57.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}笑顔が溢れるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.27,0:23:02.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}冗談混じりで頷く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:06.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}何気ないありふれたやり取りが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:11.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}心のメモリア
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:14.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}涙が零れても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:16.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}頑張れるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:20.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}君がくれた今日が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:23.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}優しくてありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:24.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Let's hang out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:29.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I wanna talk with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.81,0:22:19.61,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}約好的時間是幾點（十點）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:21.77,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}在車站前集合（OK）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:25.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}到了就告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:27.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}能夠拿用慣了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:29.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}來交談心事的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:33.66,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}實在讓人舒心愛憐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:37.71,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}獨自藏在自己心裡的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:41.96,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}過得不順 越來越多的煩心事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:48.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}想要全都忘掉 和你一起出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:54.89,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}留在心中的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:57.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}是洋溢在臉上的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.27,0:23:02.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}是半開玩笑的點頭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:06.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}是不經意間毫不稀奇的交談
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:11.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}留在心中的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:14.41,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}哪怕淚水奪眶而出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:16.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}也能夠努力下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:20.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}你留給我的今天是如此溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:23.46,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}謝謝你
